			<div class="content" id="post-content-4092349">
									

<p>I had the same &quot;mom and pop&quot; restaurant objection. That was mitigated somewhat by this being a smaller, deliberately less upscale franchise than the flagship restaurant in 3Ports. I didn't get the luxe feel I was kinda hoping for in an Ambrose GoI format but there's at least somewhat of a lampshade on it.</p>
<p>Nonetheless, the menu items were good writing and the reviews told a fun story. This still gets my upvote.</p>

